SECTION 1 — INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY OWNERSHIP
================================================================================

This repository contains or derives from software that involves three distinct
layers of intellectual property:

1. ANTHROPIC ORIGINAL WORK
   Claude Code is a product of Anthropic, PBC. The original Claude Code CLI
   software, including all source code, algorithms, system prompts, tool
   definitions, and compiled artifacts, is the exclusive intellectual property
   of Anthropic, PBC. Anthropic retains all rights thereto. This project does
   not claim any ownership over Anthropic's original work.

   Official product: https://www.anthropic.com/claude-code
   Anthropic website: https://www.anthropic.com

2. UPSTREAM COMMUNITY WORK (claude-code-best)
   The decompiled/reverse-engineered source restoration in this codebase was
   originally undertaken by the claude-code-best community
   (https://github.com/claude-code-best/claude-code). Their work — including
   source restoration, module reconstruction, feature unlocking, and
   third-party API compatibility layers — is attributed to the contributors
   of that project. This repository builds upon their publicly available work.

3. WINDOWS PACKAGING CONTRIBUTION (this repository)
   The following files in the packaging/ directory were independently authored
   by the maintainer of this repository and represent original creative work:

     packaging/build-compile.ts     — Bun compile automation script
     packaging/build-exe.ps1        — Full pipeline orchestration script
     packaging/launcher.ps1         — Windows Terminal launcher (ps2exe)
     packaging/installer.iss        — Inno Setup installer configuration
     packaging/pkg-config.json      — Build configuration reference
     packaging/README.md            — Packaging documentation

   These files, and only these files, are the original contribution of this
   repository's maintainer.

