SECTION 2 — PERMITTED USES
================================================================================

Subject to the restrictions in Section 3, you are permitted to:

a) PERSONAL USE: Use the software solely for personal, non-commercial purposes,
   including personal productivity and personal AI-assisted development.

b) LEARNING AND RESEARCH: Study the source code to understand Claude Code's
   architecture, Bun runtime compilation, Windows packaging techniques, or
   AI CLI design patterns, for non-commercial research purposes.

c) FORK AND MODIFICATION: Fork this repository and modify the packaging scripts
   (Section 1.3 files) for your own non-commercial purposes, provided you
   retain all copyright notices and attribution.

d) ACADEMIC CITATION: Reference this project in academic or educational
   contexts with proper attribution.

