================================================================================
SECTION 6 — GOVERNING INTENT
================================================================================

This project exists for the sole purpose of enabling Windows users to run
Claude Code in a native Windows executable format, for personal learning and
research. The maintainer respects Anthropic's intellectual property and
encourages users to support Anthropic's official products.

If you are an Anthropic representative and have concerns about this project,
please contact the maintainer directly via GitHub Issues before initiating
a formal takedown process.

